title: [A Piercing Scream]
description: A subtle swirling pattern of gold and silver threads climbs the walls of this spacious, square tent.  A single golden pole in the center raises the ceiling high enough to fit even the tallest of giantkin, ornamented with a spiraling string of glittering crystal beads.
